726314f-a.text:
Caldwell Avenue (formerly Johnson Avenue), north side, between 82d Street and 82nd Place, showing an old house. Eumene L. Armbrust the collector, states this to be the M. Walter house of 1873. That would place this house about 1200 ft. west of the above location. However the writer believes this to be te H. Hettisheimer house of 1893. It is the only house on the whole of Caldwell Avenue that is
Comparable to the house seen in this view.
1923
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
